Join Aladdin and Jasmine in a brand-new Realm! An ancient artifact has blanketed the markets of Agrabah in a magical sandstorm. Help reunite Aladdin and Jasmine, save the Magic Carpet, and put a stop to the mystical dilemma once and for all. Then return to your Valley to craft your very own flying carpet. 
Transform your Valley with the new Oasis Retreat Star Path, where elegance meets tranquility, with exclusive resort-inspired fashions, decoration items, and more!

description:
The beautiful, serene landscapes of Avaris are under the threat of a powerful corrupting influence, Corrosion, as it spreads across the land. Mutating anything in its path into horrific abominations.

As a Soul Whisperer, it’s your job to travel the world, easing the people of their burdens, and fighting back against the monsters inhabiting the world. During her journey, Eline awakens to a mysterious power that may hold the answer to thwarting the oncoming apocalypse. 
Edge of Memories will be coming to PlayStation 5 in Fall 2025.
